    "costs": null,
    "actions_taken": [
      "Removed the skid plate that caused the trip hazard",
      "Extended the handrail to the deck below to prevent future incidents"
    ],
    "summary": "An injured person (IP) was paged to the Capson deck. While traversing from the catwalk to the Capson deck, the IP tripped on a tread plate, fell, and landed on his left knee. The IP's boot tip hit the tread plate causing the fall. Three hours after the incident, the IP reported hearing a pop in his knee to his supervisor.",
    "recommendations": [
      "Immediate clean-up of all spills",
      "Secure all electric cords, hoses, and/or piping out of personnel walk areas",
      "Removing small throw rugs or utilize non-skid mats to prevent slip hazards",
      "Install handrails on both sides of staircases",
      "Remove tripping hazards throughout decks and mezzanines",
      "Ensure adequate lighting for both indoors and outdoors",
      "Remove debris from walkways to prevent trip hazards",
      "Periodically inspect the condition of walkways and steps, and immediately repair any damages or concerns when discovered"
    ],
    "key_phrases": [
      "tripped on tread plate",
      "boot tip hit tread plate",
      "excessive tread wear",
      "non-slip or slip resistant soles",
      "trip hazard"
    ]
